* BMAP phase-7 IDRP: "IDRP #1 <body> IDRP" repeats the body once per comma
* element of list-valued argument #1.  EMIT (11,22,33) -> OCT 11/22/33 (octal).
       OUNAME IDRPTST
EMIT   MACRO
       IDRP   #1
       OCT    #1
       IDRP
       ENDM
       EMIT   (11,22,33)
       LDA    0
       END
